        <num>CC 2677</num>
        <heading>2677.  Crop rent</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2677.  Crop rent
When the parties to an agricultural lease agree that the rent will consist of a portion of the crops, that portion is considered at all times the property of the lessor.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=109738</p>
